        <mxCell id="qaLegend" value="Every iteration writes qa/qa-report-n.md and an ITERATION_LOG line. 2-strike rule: the same identical failure surviving two fix attempts stops the loop early. Fix re-runs follow the impact matrix (QA_GATES §4), always ending at G8 — the human only ever receives an import-ready folder." style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=11;fontStyle=2;" vertex="1" parent="1">
